Em không muốn quấy rầy.

513
00:29:14,710 --> 00:29:15,710
Tạm biệt.

514
00:29:15,710 --> 00:29:17,710
Tạm biệt.

515
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:26,190
Hexenbiests.

